channel.title: Urg... two problems with testscape
channel.description:
1. Something wrong with my compiler, when i start it up, i get this error...
Exeption in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: antilag/java Press any key to continue...
2. When i try to set my chars to admin status, i start up the server and they reset to rights = 0... Of course that could be a result of the compiler problem, but theres probobly something else im doing wrong.

item.title: Urg... two problems with testscape
item.dc:creator: @Narbscape Narbscape
item.description:
@Narbscape wrote:

You have to be logged out before you save your playerrights, make sure you logout, THEN open the char files, THEN change the rights, THEN save it, and THEN log in
